HARMONY ELECTRON said unconsolidated sales
in December fell 32.23% to NT$305,961,000 from NT$451,487,000,
according to a statement filed to the  Taiwan Stock Exchange .  (Figures are in thousands of New Taiwan dollars)  =================================================================  12/2011          12/2010
Sales            305,961          451,487    
YOY%             -32.23%   -----------------Year-to-date-----------------
Sales           5,007,206        5,356,420   
YOY%              -6.52% 
=================================================================
 